<emphasis box="[1236,1436,805,827]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. melanocephala</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[831,979,834,858]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="351 - 369" refId="ref16576" refString="Jeannel R. 1963. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale. Supplement (pp. 351 - 369). In: Deboutteville C. D. &amp; Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. 2. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." type="book chapter" year="1963">Jeannel, 1963</bibRefCitation>
