<paragraph blockId="2.[831,1437,257,2078]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">
However, after examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[1220,1276,931,955]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">types</typeStatus>
we concluded that 
<taxonomicName authority="Franz, 1996" authorityName="Franz" authorityYear="1996" box="[883,1138,963,987]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andina">
<emphasis box="[883,993,965,987]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. andina</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Franz H." box="[1005,1138,963,987]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="83 - 146" refId="ref16488" refString="Franz H. 1996. Neue Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Pselaphidenfauna von Chile und Argentinien (Coleoptera: Pselaphidae). Koleopterologische Rundschau 66: 83 - 146." type="journal article" year="1996">Franz, 1996</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Franz, 1996" authorityName="Franz" authorityYear="1996" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maiopensis">
<emphasis box="[1201,1357,965,987]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. maiopensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Franz H." pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="83 - 146" refId="ref16488" refString="Franz H. 1996. Neue Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Pselaphidenfauna von Chile und Argentinien (Coleoptera: Pselaphidae). Koleopterologische Rundschau 66: 83 - 146." type="journal article" year="1996">Franz, 1996</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
resemble members of 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1964" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1964" box="[1129,1432,995,1019]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Pseudachillia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1129,1276,997,1019]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">Pseudachillia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[1283,1432,995,1019]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="5 - 12" refId="ref16637" refString="Jeannel R. 1964. Sur quelques Pselaphides du Chili. Revue Francaise d'Entomologie 31 (1): 5 - 12." type="journal article" year="1964">Jeannel, 1964</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, while 
<taxonomicName authority="Franz 1996" authorityName="Franz" authorityYear="1996" box="[903,1241,1027,1051]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pseudangularis">
<emphasis box="[903,1102,1029,1051]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. pseudangularis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Franz H." box="[1115,1241,1027,1051]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="83 - 146" refId="ref16488" refString="Franz H. 1996. Neue Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Pselaphidenfauna von Chile und Argentinien (Coleoptera: Pselaphidae). Koleopterologische Rundschau 66: 83 - 146." type="journal article" year="1996">Franz 1996</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Franz, 1996" authorityName="Franz" authorityYear="1996" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quinteroi">
<emphasis box="[1304,1436,1029,1051]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. quinteroi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Franz H." box="[831,965,1059,1083]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="83 - 146" refId="ref16488" refString="Franz H. 1996. Neue Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Pselaphidenfauna von Chile und Argentinien (Coleoptera: Pselaphidae). Koleopterologische Rundschau 66: 83 - 146." type="journal article" year="1996">Franz, 1996</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
resemble members of 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achillidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1232,1337,1061,1083]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">Achillidia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="295 - 479" refId="ref16517" refString="Jeannel R. 1962. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale (pp. 295 - 479). In: Deboutteville C. D. &amp; Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." type="book chapter" year="1962">Jeannel, 1962</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
; we will deal in more depth with these four species as well as assess the opportunity of their transfer in our forthcoming reviews of these genera. Also, one name is placed in synonymy – 
<taxonomicName authority="Raffray, 1904" authorityName="Raffray" authorityYear="1904" box="[1110,1412,1187,1211]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="picea">
<emphasis box="[1110,1255,1189,1211]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">Achilia picea</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Raffray A." box="[1263,1412,1187,1211]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="1 - 400" refId="ref16888" refString="Raffray A. 1904. Genera et Catalogue des Pselaphides. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France 73: 1 - 400." type="journal article" year="1904">Raffray, 1904</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
= 
<taxonomicName authority="Raffray, 1904" authorityName="Raffray" authorityYear="1904" box="[831,1162,1219,1243]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elfridae">
<emphasis box="[831,1002,1221,1243]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">Achilia elfridae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Raffray A." box="[1012,1162,1219,1243]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="1 - 400" refId="ref16888" refString="Raffray A. 1904. Genera et Catalogue des Pselaphides. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France 73: 1 - 400." type="journal article" year="1904">Raffray, 1904</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1181,1284,1219,1243]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">syn. nov.</emphasis>
). As a result, the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Blanchard" baseAuthorityYear="1851" box="[876,1034,1254,1276]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cosmoptera">
<emphasis box="[876,1034,1254,1276]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. cosmoptera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group is reduced to 
<taxonomicName authority="(Blanchard, 1851)" baseAuthorityName="Blanchard" baseAuthorityYear="1851" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cosmoptera">
<emphasis box="[1277,1436,1254,1276]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. cosmoptera</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Blanchard C. E." box="[839,1038,1283,1307]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="1 - 564" refId="ref16343" refString="Blanchard C. E. 1851. Fauna Chilena, Insectos, Coleopteros. LVI. Pselafianos (pp. 561 - 564). In: Gay C., Historia fisica y politica de Chile, Zoologia. Imprimerie Maulde &amp; Renou, Paris. Vol. 5: 1 - 564 + ii, pls 1 - 32." type="journal article" year="1851">Blanchard, 1851</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Raffray, 1904" authorityName="Raffray" authorityYear="1904" box="[1076,1432,1283,1308]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="blanchardi">
<emphasis box="[1076,1240,1286,1308]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. blanchardi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Raffray A." box="[1265,1432,1283,1308]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="1 - 400" refId="ref16888" refString="Raffray A. 1904. Genera et Catalogue des Pselaphides. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France 73: 1 - 400." type="journal article" year="1904">Raffray, 1904</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Raffray, 1904" authorityName="Raffray" authorityYear="1904" box="[831,1126,1315,1340]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elfridae">
<emphasis box="[831,953,1318,1340]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. elfridae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Raffray A." box="[968,1126,1315,1340]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="1 - 400" refId="ref16888" refString="Raffray A. 1904. Genera et Catalogue des Pselaphides. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France 73: 1 - 400." type="journal article" year="1904">Raffray, 1904</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[1145,1432,1315,1340]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bifrons">
<emphasis box="[1145,1259,1318,1340]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. bifrons</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[1274,1432,1315,1339]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="295 - 479" refId="ref16517" refString="Jeannel R. 1962. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale (pp. 295 - 479). In: Deboutteville C. D. &amp; Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." type="book chapter" year="1962">Jeannel, 1962</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[831,1132,1347,1372]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="temporalis">
<emphasis box="[831,975,1350,1372]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. temporalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[983,1132,1347,1372]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="295 - 479" refId="ref16517" refString="Jeannel R. 1962. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale (pp. 295 - 479). In: Deboutteville C. D. &amp; Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." type="book chapter" year="1962">Jeannel, 1962</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[1143,1432,1347,1372]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angularis">
<emphasis box="[1143,1275,1350,1372]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. angularis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[1283,1432,1347,1372]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="295 - 479" refId="ref16517" refString="Jeannel R. 1962. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale (pp. 295 - 479). In: Deboutteville C. D. &amp; Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." type="book chapter" year="1962">Jeannel, 1962</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1963" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1963" box="[880,1238,1380,1404]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="melanocephala">
<emphasis box="[880,1076,1382,1404]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. melanocephala</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[1085,1238,1380,1404]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" pagination="351 - 369" refId="ref16576" refString="Jeannel R. 1963. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale. Supplement (pp. 351 - 369). In: Deboutteville C. D. &amp; Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. 2. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." type="book chapter" year="1963">Jeannel, 1963</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, to which we add three new species described below – i. e. 
<taxonomicName authority="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella, 2021" authorityName="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella" authorityYear="2021" box="[1296,1407,1412,1436]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="covidia" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[1296,1312,1414,1436]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1328,1407,1414,1436]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">covidia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="2" pageNumber="136" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella, 2021" authorityName="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella" authorityYear="2021" box="[876,1023,1446,1468]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pandemica" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[876,1023,1446,1468]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. pandemica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1030,1088,1444,1467]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella, 2021" authorityName="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella" authorityYear="2021" box="[1141,1294,1446,1468]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quarantena" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[1141,1294,1446,1468]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. quarantena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1301,1359,1444,1467]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
– for a total of ten species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[831,1437,257,2078]" lastBlockId="3.[151,756,257,891]" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="137" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">
The species of the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Blanchard" baseAuthorityYear="1851" box="[1059,1220,1510,1532]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cosmoptera">
<emphasis box="[1059,1220,1510,1532]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. cosmoptera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group possess the following common features: pubescence decumbent, consisting of long setae sparse over the body, and very sparse on the elytra (except in 
<emphasis box="[1165,1436,1606,1628]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[1165,1273,1606,1628]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bifrons">A. bifrons</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[1285,1432,1606,1628]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="temporalis">A. temporalis</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[878,1011,1638,1660]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angularis">
<emphasis box="[878,1011,1638,1660]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. angularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); head distinctly wider than long (only slightly wider than long in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[1109,1238,1670,1692]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angularis">
<emphasis box="[1109,1238,1670,1692]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. angularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella, 2021" authorityName="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella" authorityYear="2021" box="[1286,1436,1670,1692]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quarantena" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[1286,1436,1670,1692]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="136">A. quarantena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[831,887,1700,1724]" pageId="2" pageNumber="136" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
) with two big vertexal foveae, eyes fairly protruding and longer than temples; antennae with antennomeres III-VIII about the same width; pronotum wider than long, slightly wider than head, and with slightly convex disc, its surface smooth and shiny with some punctures; median antebasal fovea slightly smaller than lateral foveae; anterior portion of lateral margins of pronotum distinctly convergent and sinuate anteriorly; posterior portion of lateral margins of pronotum slightly convergent; basal margin of pronotum bordered with row of contiguous shallow impressions; elytra together wider than long with protruding humeri; elytral disc smooth, shiny, with very few punctures (except in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[441,578,259,281]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angularis">
<emphasis box="[441,578,259,281]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. angularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for which they are more densely punctate); elytra with two big basal foveae, sometimes with two small more medial foveae (as for example in the 
<typeStatus box="[408,501,354,378]" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1963" box="[544,740,356,378]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="melanocephala">
<emphasis box="[544,740,356,378]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. melanocephala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); sutural stria entire; elytral discal stria extended to about elytral mid-length; abdomen smooth, with some minute punctures; first abdominal tergite with diverging basal striae extending to about one-fourth of paratergal length (except in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[273,409,516,538]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angularis">
<emphasis box="[273,409,516,538]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. angularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in which they are longer than one-fourth of paratergal length), and separated at base by about one-fourth of tergal width (except in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[617,749,581,603]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angularis">
<emphasis box="[617,749,581,603]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. angularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella, 2021" authorityName="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella" authorityYear="2021" box="[151,303,613,635]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pandemica" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[151,303,613,635]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. pandemica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[316,379,611,634]" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1963" box="[441,639,613,635]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="melanocephala">
<emphasis box="[441,639,613,635]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. melanocephala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, in which they are wider than one-fourth of tergal width); short and sparse setal brush between basal striae. Many specimens of both sexes of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Blanchard" baseAuthorityYear="1851" box="[322,475,709,731]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cosmoptera">
<emphasis box="[322,475,709,731]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. cosmoptera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Raffray" authorityYear="1904" box="[487,599,709,731]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elfridae">
<emphasis box="[487,599,709,731]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. elfridae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella, 2021" authorityName="Kurbatov &amp; Cuccodoro &amp; Sabella" authorityYear="2021" box="[611,756,709,731]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pandemica" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[611,756,709,731]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. pandemica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[151,210,739,762]" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[266,399,741,763]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angularis">
<emphasis box="[266,399,741,763]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="137">A. angularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
bear also a bundle of long setae on lateral side of first visible abdominal sternite (see 
